  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n                                                            \n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Jul 20, 2026 at 06:28 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>Mumbai: <a href=\"/tag/merck\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Merck</a> India has partnered with the <a href=\"/tag/nmims+school+of+pharmacy+%26+technology+management\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NMIMS School of Pharmacy &amp; Technology Management</a> (SPPSPTM) to launch the <a href=\"/tag/catalyst+programme\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CATALYST programme</a>, an industry-academia initiative designed to prepare students for the evolving demands of the pharmaceutical and healthcare sectors.According to NMIMS, the 12-week certification programme will equip students with industry-relevant knowledge through intensive modules spanning various scientific domains.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>The programme is designed to complement classroom learning with real-world industry exposure and familiarise students with global pharmaceutical practices and the competencies expected in today's workplace, NMIMS said in a press release.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>Drawing on Merck's expertise in Global Capability Centres (GCCs), which support key global pharmaceutical functions, the programme will expose students to internationally aligned processes and help them develop the technical, regulatory, and professional capabilities required for global roles, the institution added.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>NMIMS and Merck plan to conduct multiple editions of the CATALYST programme annually, with participants receiving a certification upon successful completion.\"Since its launch, the CATALYST Programme has been successfully completed with two of our academic partners. Our latest collaboration with NMIMS SPPSPTM builds on that momentum by introducing students to contemporary pharmaceutical R&amp;D practices and the evolving needs of Global Capability Centres. By investing early in capability building and creating meaningful industry exposure, we can shape a workforce that is skilled, confident, and ready to lead the future of healthcare,\" said Suneela Thatte, Vice President, Merck Healthcare R&amp;D India.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Jul 20, 2026 at 06:28 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Jul 20, 2026 at 06:28 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">1 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"top-newsletter-subs__icon-nl\" role=\"presentation\" aria-label=\"Newsletter icon\">\n                <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-newsletter.svg\" alt=\"Newsletter icon\" width=\"55\" height=\"55\">\n            </figure> -->\n        \n            \n                \n                    <h2>All about ETHealthworld industry right on your smartphone! </h2>\n                    <ul>\n                        <li><a href=\"/app\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Download the ETHealthworld App</a> and get the Realtime updates and Save your favourite articles.</li>\n                    </ul>\n                                            <!-- <div class=\"app-store-container desktop-view\">\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"\" aria-label=\"Play Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" src=\"https://st.etb2bimg.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/icon-g-play.png\" alt=\"\" />\n                            </a>\n                            <a href=\"/app\" title=\"App Store\">\n                                <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\